  "title": "Tropical Brazilian Sugar Snap Peas Tagine",
  "description": "A flavorful and festive Brazilian dish featuring sugar snap peas, cooked in a stone bowl dolsot style tajine clay vessel, perfect for a dairy free friendly meal. This resinous and shaggy dish is sure to delight.",
